Install using:
$ make install

Copy the sample-configuration:
$ cp /usr/local/share/doc/juniper/juniper.conf.sample /etc/juniper.conf

Edit username/password in configuration-file!

Start the tunnel using:
$ sudo /etc/init.d/juniper start

Logs can be found in:
$ cat ~root/.pulse_secure/pulse/pulsesvc.log

Beware that resolv.conf and routes may be overwritten by dhcp-clients 
and NetworkManager.

pulsesvc was extracted from https://bouvetasa.sharepoint.com/Bouvet%20public/Download/VPN%20klient%20for%20ssl.bouvet.no/Linux/pulse-8.1R8.i386.deb
